COMPILING
=========

If you are on a Unix system and have gcc in your path, just hit 'make' and
you should be done. Otherwise you are forced to figure it out yourself. 

NOTE: If you get a bunch of weird error messages, make sure that the
Makefile and the source file are in Unix text format and do not have DOS
carriage returns at the end of each line.

